map <S-Right> <C-W><Right>
map <F9> <ESC>:Tagbar<CR>
map <C-p> <ESC>"+p
map <C-y> "+y
map <C-Up> 10<Up>
map <C-Down> 10<Down>
map <F10> <ESC>:NERDTreeToggle<CR>

